                             'Tri' 1.12

                         by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Tri' is a Workbench @{"game" link play} played on a triangular-shaped board where
a chain of 6 links, that cannot be splitted, is displayed. The goal
is to move the links, following certain @{"rules" link play} in order to match a
triangular or hexagonal pattern shown at the upper right in the game
window.

